00:35:09,070 --> 00:35:09,760
I'm going to...

617
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:48,880
Alright, we're at your place.

618
00:35:48,880 --> 00:35:50,000
Hurry and go back.

619
00:35:55,190 --> 00:35:56,840
What about you?

620
00:35:59,070 --> 00:36:01,670
