622
00:36:04,630 --> 00:36:06,630
I can go and explain to the police.

623
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:07,880
What's there to explain?

624
00:36:08,230 --> 00:36:09,230
Remember,

625
00:36:09,230 --> 00:36:10,110
