627
00:36:12,710 --> 00:36:13,710
You have nothing to do with it.

628
00:36:13,710 --> 00:36:14,400
Got it?

629
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:17,110
But you were just helping me.

630
00:36:17,110 --> 00:36:18,920
Stop yapping.

631
00:36:18,920 --> 00:36:20,710
