it has nothing to do with you.

632
00:36:21,230 --> 00:36:22,630
Since they laid hands on me,

633
00:36:23,030 --> 00:36:24,480
it's my business with them now.

634
00:36:25,670 --> 00:36:26,670
Be good, go home.

635
00:36:40,110 --> 00:36:41,550
