645
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:33,880
Just kidding.

646
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:35,510
Think about it.

647
00:37:35,880 --> 00:37:37,480
What have we been through?

648
00:37:37,920 --> 00:37:40,000
