669
00:39:11,110 --> 00:39:11,920
I'll make a call.

670
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:25,840
What are you doing?

671
00:39:26,670 --> 00:39:27,590
They're your friends,

672
00:39:27,590 --> 00:39:29,190
