676
00:39:39,070 --> 00:39:40,880
Yifei, let me tell you the truth.

677
00:39:41,630 --> 00:39:43,360
I didn't get this from your dad.

678
00:39:45,630 --> 00:39:47,630
Your mom gave it to me

679
00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:48,550
as a debt payment.

680
00:39:49,360 --> 00:39:50,190
Get it?

681
00:40:01,510 --> 00:40:02,110
Dai Wei.

682
00:40:03,070 --> 00:40:04,630
If you have something to say,
say it properly.

683
00:40:05,070 --> 00:40:06,150
Why did you deceive me
and bring me here?

684
00:40:06,150 --> 00:40:07,880
I didn't deceive you, Yifei.

685
00:40:08,190 --> 00:40:10,630
I just sincerely wanted
to spend some time with you

686
00:40:10,630 --> 00:40:12,190
and catch up with you.
What's wrong with that?

687
00:40:13,710 --> 00:40:15,000
Yifei, did you know?

688
00:40:15,960 --> 00:40:17,510
All these years in prison,

689
00:40:17,510 --> 00:40:19,400
the only reason I persisted
was because I thought I could

690
00:40:20,710 --> 00:40:22,590
see you again when I get out.

691
00:40:23,110 --> 00:40:24,280
The first thing I did when I got out

692
00:40:24,280 --> 00:40:26,150
was to go to your school
to see you go to school and leave school

693
00:40:26,150 --> 00:40:27,070
and watch you practice dancing.

694
00:40:28,440 --> 00:40:29,110
I thought

695
00:40:29,630 --> 00:40:31,030
we could be together now that I'm out.

696
00:40:31,060 --> 00:40:32,620
Did you forget how I got in?

697
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:34,320
Or do you not need me anymore

698
00:40:34,320 --> 00:40:35,550
now that you've grown up?

699
00:40:39,150 --> 00:40:39,880
I have something to do.

700
00:40:40,150 --> 00:40:40,760
I have to go.

701
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:15,670
Her phone's still off.

702
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:19,630
Stop pacing in front of me,

703
00:41:19,630 --> 00:41:20,630
