704
00:41:20,630 --> 00:41:22,150
You're making me anxious.

705
00:41:22,150 --> 00:41:23,440
I can't get through.

706
00:41:28,630 --> 00:41:30,320
We can't keep waiting like this.

707
00:41:30,630 --> 00:41:31,510
Let's call the police.

708
00:41:32,110 --> 00:41:32,550
Yes.

709
00:41:32,550 --> 00:41:33,320
Yes, call the police.

710
00:41:36,280 --> 00:41:37,000
Yifei.

711
00:41:38,110 --> 00:41:38,880
Yifei.

712
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:39,800
Where did you go?

713
00:41:40,110 --> 00:41:41,230
We searched for you all night yesterday.

714
00:41:42,510 --> 00:41:43,550
I didn't go anywhere.

715
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:45,920
I went out to hang out with my friends.

716
00:41:48,480 --> 00:41:49,960
We searched everywhere last night.

717
00:41:49,960 --> 00:41:51,070
Who did you go out with?

718
00:41:51,760 --> 00:41:52,760
Friends from the dance troupe.

719
00:41:53,150 --> 00:41:54,070
You don't know them.

720
00:41:54,510 --> 00:41:55,480
Friends from the dance troupe?

721
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:58,070
Which friends from the dance troupe?

722
00:41:59,630 --> 00:42:01,070
I have to help my grandma at the shop.

723
00:42:01,480 --> 00:42:02,880
Go home first, guys.

724
00:42:03,440 --> 00:42:03,960
Yifei.

725
00:42:04,070 --> 00:42:04,440
How about

726
00:42:04,800 --> 00:42:06,000
you go upstairs and rest?

727
00:42:06,000 --> 00:42:07,000
We'll take care of this.

728
00:42:07,630 --> 00:42:08,440
Yeah, let me handle it.

729
00:42:08,840 --> 00:42:10,030
Yes, take a break.

730
00:42:10,030 --> 00:42:10,440
That's enough!

731
00:42:10,440 --> 00:42:12,150
I told you, I'm really okay!

732
00:42:13,400 --> 00:42:14,880
Can't you believe it?

733
00:42:15,760 --> 00:42:16,360
Yifei, you...

734
00:42:16,360 --> 00:42:16,840
Enough.

735
00:42:16,840 --> 00:42:18,230
Yifei said she's fine.

736
00:42:18,670 --> 00:42:19,800
Stop asking.

737
00:42:20,070 --> 00:42:21,510
