738
00:42:25,230 --> 00:42:26,880
Are you going to
the graduation party tonight?

739
00:42:28,760 --> 00:42:29,360
Of course,

740
00:42:29,880 --> 00:42:30,760
I'll go.

741
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:41,550
