743
00:42:42,550 --> 00:42:44,230
Cheers!

744
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:48,630
Tingting.

745
00:42:49,960 --> 00:42:51,590
We're going to the same city.

746
00:42:51,840 --> 00:42:53,550
Let's stay in touch more often.

747
00:42:53,760 --> 00:42:54,280
Fatty,

748
00:42:54,590 --> 00:42:55,480
if you don't confess now,

749
00:42:55,630 --> 00:42:57,110
