764
00:43:22,880 --> 00:43:23,550
Yeah.

765
00:43:24,000 --> 00:43:25,360
You grew up together.

766
00:43:26,030 --> 00:43:27,360
You'll still keep in touch.

767
00:43:27,920 --> 00:43:28,710
