769
00:43:30,920 --> 00:43:31,360
Go over there.

770
00:43:31,550 --> 00:43:31,960
Go over there.

771
00:43:32,070 --> 00:43:32,590
Shoo.

772
00:43:32,920 --> 00:43:34,030
